data.description: Delightful open concept 1bed/1bath in a fascinating Lakeshore East neighborhood!! A rare downtown cul-de-sac! This ample unit offers newly remodeled kitchen and bathroom, updated vinyl plank flooring, plenty 3 closet spaces, and more. This building has the amazing full amenity luxury.  400 Health and Spa"-racquetball, basketball, ping-pong, year-round sunny indoor pool jacuzzi-sun deck, party room, business center, library, children's playroom, cardio, machine weights, laundry, massage therapist, steam, sauna, and whirlpool! (3) bike rooms and more... Walking distance to Maggie Daley Park, Lakeshore East Dog Park, Millennium Park, 3 blocks from Michigan Ave, Mariano's, tons of restaurants, and everything Downtown Chicago's city and lakefront have to offer. Watch the sunrise and weekly summer fireworks on the east-facing 18 ft balcony with lake views! Schedule your appointment and come see the exciting "New Eastside" neighborhood. 30 min free guess parking. This Is a short sale.
